  <skiResortDescription><![CDATA[<div class="c-page-content">
<p>Whether you are seeking the <a data-udi="umb://document/3d2e5b1e3fb14ecd863a5723d5c4fc55" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3d2e5b1e3fb14ecd863a5723d5c4fc55}" title="Insider's Guide: Best High Altitude Ski Resorts">highest</a> or most <a data-udi="umb://document/b28019985984419899535b05fb4b9b57" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b28019985984419899535b05fb4b9b57}" title="Insider’s Guide: Top 10 snow-sure ski resorts in Europe">snow sure ski resorts</a>, we have over 70 resorts across 6 different countries to suit everyone, from <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ski-holidays/ski-holiday-types/family-ski-holidays">families</a>, groups to solo skiers. </p>
<p>All our resorts offer great skiing and <a data-udi="umb://document/13cca02f7ef4467cade8c8e89e68fe39" href="/{localLink:umb://document/13cca02f7ef4467cade8c8e89e68fe39}" title="Snowboarding Holidays">snowboarding</a> for all abilities and lots of additional extras from <a data-udi="umb://document/e4565aae9d704cf59edeca5aba507d16" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e4565aae9d704cf59edeca5aba507d16}" title="Ski Lessons">ski lessons</a>, ice skating to snowshoeing.</p>
<p>Every resort has been selected to suit all types of skiers - whether you are looking for a busy town with lots of shops and cafes, a peaceful resort with <a data-udi="umb://document/b4c9b6c332ba475d8d2f9f940dba4d46" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b4c9b6c332ba475d8d2f9f940dba4d46}" title="Ski &amp; Spa Holidays">spa hotels</a> and fine-dining restaurants or a lively area with fun <a data-udi="umb://document/89595b9898014c5fbd93f5619c64b079" href="/{localLink:umb://document/89595b9898014c5fbd93f5619c64b079}" title="Apres Ski Holidays">après bars</a>. Below you'll find just a few of our favourites...</p>
</div>]]></skiResortDescription>
